news.title: OMBR Layout: Court restores acquired land favouring Bengaluru development body
news.para: On March 31, 2016, a single bench held that physical possession of the land in question (about 2.5 acres) was not taken and hence, the acquisition had lapsed and section 24(2) of the new Land Acquisition Act (of 2013) would apply.

news.title: Pune civic body to start survey of STPs in big housing societies
news.para: The administration has given directives to housing complexes to treat sewage on their premises. Societies not operating treatment plants properly will be fined.

news.title: About 20 lakh buildings in Kerala were out of property tax net in 2021
news.para: Local bodies exempted 19.8 lakh residential buildings below 660sq ft from paying property tax in the state, accounting for 13% of total buildings as per the data collected in 2021.
